OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry start to
OL,6,Fthe evening with long clear spells.
OL,7,FTurning cloudier later in the evening
OL,8,Fand overnight with few showers
OL,9,Fpossible, but still plenty of dry and
OL,10,Fclear intervals.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FSunny intervals with patchy
OL,13,Fcloud and a few showers in the morning
OL,14,Fbut these dying out to leave a dry
OL,15,Fafternoon with long spells of
OL,16,Fsunshine. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
